## Risk Assessment

| Risk | Severity | Mitigation |
|------|----------|------------|
| **Import path breakage** | High | Systematic find-and-replace; TypeScript compiler will catch missing imports |
| **Android native project path issues** | Medium | Verify `settings.gradle` and `build.gradle` after moving `android/` to root |
| **iOS native project path issues** | Medium | Verify `Podfile` paths after moving `ios/` to root |
| **Redux state shape change** | Low | Only `state.sdk` в†’ `state.app` rename; all selectors updated together |
| **Mock в†’ API switch regression** | Low | `USE_MOCK` flag ensures mock path stays functional |
| **RTK Query cache invalidation** | Low | Tag types preserved as-is |
| **Lost functionality in repository removal** | Medium | AssessmentRepository has significant logic (API + mock fallback + grading); must be fully absorbed into assessmentApi |

